{"id": 243228732, "title": "Rich Paul: Bronny James 'Deserves to Be' in NBA with LeBron, Lakers After 2024 Draft", "text": "Bronny James' agent Rich Paul believes his client has earned the shot to play in the NBA regardless of the fact that he is the son of Los Angeles Lakers star LeBron James. \"He's got just as much to prove as anybody that was drafted with him Thursday,\" Paul told TMZ Sports. Paul added: \"He deserves to be in the NBA.\" The Lakers drafted 19-year-old James with the No. 55 pick of the 2024 NBA Draft following his freshman season at USC. James made his comeback from offseason heart surgery in December to average 4.8 points in 25 games, mostly off the bench. This article will be updated soon to provide more information and analysis. For more from Bleacher Report on this topic and from around the sports world, check out our B/R app, homepage and social feeds\u2014including Twitter, Instagram, Facebook and TikTok.", "summary": "Bronny James' agent Rich Paul believes his client has earned the shot to play in the NBA regardless of the fact that he is the son of Los Angeles Lakers star\u2026", "url": "https://bleacherreport.com/articles/10126543-rich-paul-bronny-james-deserves-to-be-in-nba-with-lebron-lakers-after-2024-draft", "image": "https://media.bleacherreport.com/image/upload/v1719621811/hqq7wndecl0ji8szc33o.jpg", "video": null, "publish_date": "2024-06-29 00:44:07", "author": "Julia Stumbaugh", "authors": ["Julia Stumbaugh"], "language": "en", "source_country": "US", "sentiment": 0.446}